OL,3,CCouncil tax: Government to review
OL,4,C'aggressive' debt collection methods
OL,6,FVulnerable people who fall behind on
OL,7,Ftheir council tax bills could be
OL,8,Fbetter protected, under plans being
OL,9,Fconsidered by the government.
OL,11,FLaunching a consultation on the
OL,12,Fadministration of council tax, the
OL,13,Fgovernment said they are reviewing the
OL,14,Fdebt enforcement processes, including
OL,15,Fthe use of bailiffs, in a bid to end
OL,16,F"unacceptable" and "aggressive"
OL,17,Fpractices.
