OL,6,FThe government said they will look at
OL,7,F"a more appropriate and proportionate
OL,8,Ftimeframe" before councils can demand
OL,9,Fa full bill from households.
OL,11,FCurrently, when someone fails to pay
OL,12,Fcouncil tax, a reminder can be sent
OL,13,Fseven days after a missed payment.
OL,15,FFollowing that, if the bill remains
OL,16,Funpaid seven days after the reminder
OL,17,Fnotice has been issued, the full
OL,18,Famount due for the year becomes
OL,19,Fpayable.
