OL,6,FThe council may also seek a liability
OL,7,Forder to confirm the debt and start
OL,8,Fenforcement action.
OL,10,FThe government is seeking views on
OL,11,Fwhen full liability should apply,
OL,12,Ffollowing a reminder notice being
OL,13,Fissued, and whether there are any
OL,14,Ffurther steps councils should take
OL,15,Fbefore being able to charge for a full
OL,16,Fyear's bill.
