OL,6,FThe consultation document said: "It is
OL,7,Fcritical councils have the power to
OL,8,Frecover unpaid council tax and many
OL,9,Fcouncils do good work to support local
OL,10,Fpeople.
OL,12,F"However, the government believes that
OL,13,Faggressive recovery action has been
OL,14,Fapplied too quickly and too intensely
OL,15,Fin some cases."
OL,17,FMinister for Local Government and
OL,18,FEnglish Devolution, Jim McMahon, said:
OL,19,F"We are listening and taking action to
OL,20,Fmake council tax fairer, more
OL,21,Ftransparent and easier to manage.
