OL,6,F"Council Tax rapid and aggressive debt
OL,7,Fcollection methods currently hurt
OL,8,Fmillions and disproportionately affect
OL,9,Fthose with mental health problems," he
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,F"The government has listened to our
OL,13,Fevidence, and this consultation
OL,14,Fthankfully looks at slowing it down,
OL,15,Fadding-in consideration, capping added
OL,16,Fcosts, and pointing people towards
OL,17,Fhelp to pay."
OL,19,FCitizens Advice also welcomed the
OL,20,Freview.
