OL,3,CCouncil tax: Government to review
OL,4,C'aggressive' debt collection methods
OL,6,F"Council tax is our second biggest
OL,7,Fdebt query area, narrowly behind
OL,8,Fenergy arrears," a spokesperson said.
OL,10,F"And a quarter of clients with council
OL,11,Ftax arrears need advice about dealing
OL,12,Fwith bailiffs, which can be a
OL,13,Fterrifying experience.
OL,15,F"Current rules mean small debts
OL,16,Fquickly spiral out of control -
OL,17,Fworsening hardship rather than
OL,18,Fproviding the support people need to
OL,19,Fget back on their feet."
