OL,6,FThe Chair of the Local Government
OL,7,FAssociation's Economy and Resources
OL,8,FBoard, Cllr Pete Marland, said while
OL,9,Fthey understand people can be affected
OL,10,Fby debt, they have a "wide range of
OL,11,Fmeasures to ensure that recovery
OL,12,Fpractices are fair, and support is
OL,13,Favailable for households who are
OL,14,Fstruggling to pay their bills."
