OL,6,FHe added that they will work with the
OL,7,Fgovernment on an approach that
OL,8,F"enables councils to invest in council
OL,9,Ftax collection practices that
OL,10,Feffectively balance the collection of
OL,11,Fvital revenues with measures that help
OL,12,Fthose struggling to pay."
OL,14,FOther parts of the consultation will
OL,15,Finclude moving billing to 12 monthly
OL,16,Fpayments by default, rather than
OL,17,Fspread out across 10 months to help
OL,18,Fhouseholds spread the cost over a
OL,19,Flonger period.
